{"article_id":"232cmv3Zzx8MyEsb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Pope Benedict XVI surprises the world with his decision","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to step down","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"He says","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"his strength in the past few months `` has deteriorated ''","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"A new pope should be chosen by Easter ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"a spokesman says","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"No more than 117 cardinals will select the next pontiff","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"The spiritual leader of 1.2 billion Roman Catholics , Pope Benedict XVI , surprised the world Monday","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"by saying","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"he will resign at the end of the month","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"`` because of advanced age . '' It 's the first time","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"a pope has stepped down in nearly 600 years .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"`` Strength of mind and body are necessary , strength","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"which in the last few months has deteriorated in me to the extent","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"that I have had to recognize my incapacity","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"to adequately fulfill the ministry","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"entrusted to me , ''","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"said Benedict , 85 ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"according to the Vatican .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"The news startled the Catholic world","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and led to frenzied speculation","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"about who would replace him ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"including a debate about the merits","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"of naming a pontiff from the developing world ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"where the church continues to grow ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"versus one from Europe ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"where it has deep historical roots .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"But that decision will not be made by Benedict ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"who will leave his post at 8 p.m. on February 28 ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"said the Rev . Federico Lombardi , a Vatican spokesman .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Watch Pope Benedict XVI resign","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Watch Pope Benedict XVI resign 00:10","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"JUST WATCHED Gibney :","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Abuse defines Benedict 's papacy","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"MUST WATCH Gibney :","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Abuse defines Benedict 's papacy","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"02:21","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Pope Benedict and the sex abuse scandal","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"MUST WATCH Pope Benedict and the sex abuse scandal 02:30","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"`` Before Easter , we will have the new pope , ''","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"While Benedict wo n't be directly involved in his successor 's selection ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"his influence will undoubtedly be felt .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"He appointed 67 of the 117 cardinals","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"-- as of Monday -- are set","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"to make the decision .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"The number of electors could drop to 115 ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"as two cardinals will turn 80 in March ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"when their age makes them ineligible","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"to cast a vote .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"More than two thirds of whatever the final number must agree on the next pope , a decision","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that will be announced to the world in the form a puff of white smoke","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"emerging from a chimney in the Vatican .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"CNN Senior Vatican Analyst John Allen said","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"that means the next pope ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"no matter where he is from ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"will probably continue in Benedict 's conservative tradition ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"which has seen the church take a firm line on issues such as abortion , birth control and divorce .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"The pope ,","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"born Joseph Ratzinger ,","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"will first head to the pope 's summer residence","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"before he likely retires to a monastery","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"and devotes himself to a life of reflection and prayer ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"Lombardi said .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"He wo n't be involved in managing the church after his resignation .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"In a sign of just how rare an event this is ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"church officials are n't sure","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"what the pope will be called","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"after he leaves the office .","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"While not quite unprecedented ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"his resignation is certainly historic .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"The last pope","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"to step down before his death","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"was Gregory XII ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"who in 1415 quit","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"to end a civil war within the church","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"in which more than one man claimed to be pope .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"Benedict took months","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"to decide","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that he was n't up for the job anymore ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Lombardi said .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"`` It 's not a decision","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"he has just improvised , ''","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"the Vatican spokesman said .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"A family friend in Regensburg , Germany , told CNN","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"that Benedict had been thinking resigning for some time","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"because of his age .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"He had discussed the decision with his older brother , the Rev . Georg Ratzinger ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"according to the friend ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"who asked not to be named","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"because he does not speak for Georg Ratzinger .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"The health of Pope Benedict XVI","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"The health of Pope Benedict XVI","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"00:59","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Pope cites 'advanced age ' in resignation","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"Pope cites 'advanced age ' in resignation","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"04:29","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Pope explains why he 's resigning","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"Pope explains","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"why he 's resigning","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"01:43","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Several years ago , Benedict had suggested","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"he would be open to resigning","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"should his health fail ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Allen said .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"But no one expected him to do so this soon .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"Jannet Walsh , a CNN iReporter from Murdock , Minnesota , counts herself among those `` shocked '' by the news of his resignation .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"But she said","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"it was an admirable decision","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"because he seemingly recognized","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"that he could not adequately `` carry out his office as pope ''","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"given his health .","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"`` The resignation of the pope is actually a very selfless act ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"and it should be applauded , ''","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"Walsh said .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"Joseph Ratzinger was born and raised in Germany ,","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"where he briefly served in the Hitler Youth ,","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"despite his objections ,","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"and the German military during World War II .","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"He then established himself as a leading theologian , professor and local Catholic leader","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"before rising up the Vatican ranks .","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"He was dean of the College of Cardinals in 2005","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"when he became the sixth German","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"to be picked as pope ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"albeit the first since the 11th century .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"At the time , the church was facing several pressing issues ,","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"including declining popularity in parts of the world and a growing crisis over the church 's role","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"in handling molestation accusations against priests around the world .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Given his age at the time","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"-- 78 --","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"he was widely seen as a caretaker pope , a bridge to the next generation after the long tenure of John Paul II , a popular , globe-trotting pontiff","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"whose early youth and vigor gave way to such frailty in later years","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"that he required help walking","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"and was often hard to hear during public addresses .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"As an aide to John Paul , Benedict served as a strict enforcer of his conservative social doctrine .","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"To no one 's surprise , he continued to espouse a conservative doctrine","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"after taking the office himself .","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"He frequently warned of a `` dictatorship of relativism . ''","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"`` In a world","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"which he considered relativist and secular and so on ,","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"his main thrust was to re-establish a sense of Catholic identity for Catholics themselves , ''","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"said Delia Gallagher , contributing editor for Inside the Vatican magazine .","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"Not everyone embraced this conservatism .","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"CNN iReporter Egberto Willies , a former Catholic , said","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"positions such as opposing the distribution of condoms","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"to curb the AIDS epidemic in Africa","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"shows how `` outdated '' the church under Benedict was .","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"`` This is a pope","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"that was so conservative","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"that many of his values simply , in today 's world , made no sense , ''","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"said Willies , a resident of Kingwood , Texas .","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"Bill Donohue , of the conservative U.S. Catholic League , credited Benedict for working to reduce friction among adherents of various faiths , something","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"that was a key part of John Paul 's mission as well .","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"`` The pope made it clear","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"that religious freedom was not only a God-given right ,","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"it was 'the path to peace , ' ''","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"Donohue said .","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"But Mohammed Shafiq , chief executive of the Ramadhan Foundation , offered a different take .","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"He referenced a 2006 speech","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"Benedict made","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"in which he quoted from 14th century Byzantine emperor Manuel II Paleologus","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"the Muslim Prophet Mohammed brought into the world `` things only evil and inhuman . ''","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"These remarks spurred protests by Muslims worldwide and an apology from the pope .","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"`` This sadly meant the hard work of his predecessor Pope John Paul II was tarnished","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"and required extensive work","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"to rebuild ties between Christianity and Islam , ''","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"Shafiq said .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"`` That is something","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":"he has tried to do over the past eight years ,","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"and we do wish","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"it could have started better","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"than it did . ''","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"In his tone , demeanor and actions , Benedict was notably different from his predecessor .","depth":7},{"id":191,"text":"Where John Paul wowed crowds around the world with his mastery of numerous languages ,","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"Benedict 's influence will be felt through his writings , part of his training as a college professor ,","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"Gallagher said .","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"Benedict became pope at the height of the molestation scandal","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"involving Catholic priests ,","depth":9},{"id":196,"text":"with complaints of sexual abuse and lawsuits over the issue","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"tearing at the church","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"and threatening its moral standing around the world .","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"In 2008 , he acknowledged `` the shame","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"which we have all felt ''","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"over abuse reports","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"those responsible for the `` evils '' should face justice .","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"Two years later in 2010","depth":13},{"id":205,"text":"-- the same year","depth":14},{"id":206,"text":"that he issued new rules","depth":15},{"id":207,"text":"aimed at stopping abuse --","depth":15},{"id":208,"text":"he said","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"abusive priests `` disfigured their ministry ''","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"and brought `` profound shame and regret '' on the church .","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"The new rules included allowing church prosecution of suspected molesters for 20 years after the incidents occurred ,","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"up from 10 years previously .","depth":12},{"id":213,"text":"The rules also made it a church crime to download child pornography","depth":12},{"id":214,"text":"and allowed the pope to remove a priest","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"without a formal Vatican trial .","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"`` No one did more","depth":12},{"id":217,"text":"to successfully address the problem of priestly sexual abuse than Joseph Ratzinger , ''","depth":12},{"id":218,"text":"Donohue said .","depth":11},{"id":219,"text":"But others","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"-- such as Barbara Blaine , president of Survivors Network of those","depth":15},{"id":221,"text":"Abused by Priests --","depth":15},{"id":222,"text":"say","depth":13},{"id":223,"text":"the opposite is true .","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"`` I would hate for him to be remembered as someone","depth":14},{"id":225,"text":"who did the right thing","depth":14},{"id":226,"text":"because from our perspective , Pope Benedict 's record has been abysmal , ''","depth":13},{"id":227,"text":"Blaine said .","depth":12},{"id":228,"text":"In 2010 , The New York Times reported","depth":10},{"id":229,"text":"that church officials ,","depth":12},{"id":230,"text":"including Ratzinger ,","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"had failed to act in the case of a Wisconsin priest","depth":12},{"id":232,"text":"accused of molesting up to 200 boys .","depth":12},{"id":233,"text":"The Times reported","depth":11},{"id":234,"text":"that church officials stopped proceedings against the priest","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"after he wrote Ratzinger ,","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"who was at the time the cardinal in charge of the group","depth":12},{"id":237,"text":"that oversees Catholic Church doctrine .","depth":12},{"id":238,"text":"Ratzinger never answered the letter ,","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"according to the Times ,","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"and church officials have said","depth":11},{"id":241,"text":"he had no knowledge of the situation .","depth":11},{"id":242,"text":"But a lawyer","depth":12},{"id":243,"text":"who obtained internal church paperwork","depth":12},{"id":244,"text":"said at the time","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"that it `` shows a direct line from the victims through the bishops and directly to the man","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"who is now pope . ''","depth":11},{"id":247,"text":"Also in 2010 , the Times reported","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"that the future pope","depth":12},{"id":249,"text":"-- while serving as the archbishop in Munich --","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"had been copied on a memo","depth":11},{"id":251,"text":"informing him","depth":11},{"id":252,"text":"that a priest","depth":13},{"id":253,"text":"accused of molesting children","depth":13},{"id":254,"text":"was being returned to pastoral work .","depth":12},{"id":255,"text":"At the time , a spokesman for the archdiocese said","depth":9},{"id":256,"text":"Ratzinger received hundreds of memos a year ,","depth":10},{"id":257,"text":"and it was highly unlikely that he had read it .","depth":10},{"id":258,"text":"Victims ' groups are pressing the International Criminal Court to prosecute Benedict in the sex abuse scandal","depth":7},{"id":259,"text":"and say","depth":8},{"id":260,"text":"the resignation wo n't change that ,","depth":8},{"id":261,"text":"according to Pam Spees , of the public policy law firm Center for Constitutional Rights ,","depth":7},{"id":262,"text":"which is helping SNAP pursue the case .","depth":7},{"id":263,"text":"In a statement","depth":10},{"id":264,"text":"issued Monday ,","depth":10},{"id":265,"text":"Blaine said","depth":9},{"id":266,"text":"the church should choose a new pope","depth":10},{"id":267,"text":"dedicated to preventing sexual abuse by priests .","depth":10},{"id":268,"text":"`` For the church to truly embody the spiritual teachings of Jesus Christ ,","depth":10},{"id":269,"text":"it must be led by a pontiff","depth":11},{"id":270,"text":"who demands transparency ,","depth":12},{"id":271,"text":"exposes child-molesting clerics ,","depth":13},{"id":272,"text":"punishes wrongdoers and enablers ,","depth":14},{"id":273,"text":"cooperates with law enforcement","depth":15},{"id":274,"text":"and makes true amends to those","depth":16},{"id":275,"text":"who were hurt so greatly by Catholic priests , employees and volunteers , ''","depth":16},{"id":276,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":277,"text":"For others , the next pope must be someone","depth":8},{"id":278,"text":"who not only can satisfactorily address this scandal and other issues ,","depth":9},{"id":279,"text":"but he also must be able to speak to all Catholics and others","depth":11},{"id":280,"text":"-- especially younger people --","depth":11},{"id":281,"text":"in a way","depth":11},{"id":282,"text":"that resonates with them .","depth":11},{"id":283,"text":"`` I know","depth":10},{"id":284,"text":"that my grandparents think of the whole church a little bit differently","depth":11},{"id":285,"text":"than my generation does , ''","depth":11},{"id":286,"text":"said Kaleigh Forst , a student , in New York City .","depth":9},{"id":287,"text":"`` I feel","depth":9},{"id":288,"text":"like we could use somebody maybe a little younger ,","depth":10},{"id":289,"text":"that has a new perspective . ''","depth":10},{"id":290,"text":"Whatever his past , few expected Benedict to announce","depth":8},{"id":291,"text":"he was stepping down ,","depth":8},{"id":292,"text":"including world and Catholic leaders ,","depth":8},{"id":293,"text":"who voiced admiration for his decision and the man himself .","depth":8},{"id":294,"text":"U.S. Vice President Joe Biden , himself a Catholic , said","depth":9},{"id":295,"text":"he thought","depth":10},{"id":296,"text":"the pope set `` an incredibly high standard ''","depth":11},{"id":297,"text":"by understanding his own limitations and how they might affect the church .","depth":11},{"id":298,"text":"`` The decision reinforces for me as a practicing Catholic","depth":11},{"id":299,"text":"that this is a man of great integrity","depth":12},{"id":300,"text":"and looking out for what he believes is in the best interest of our church , ''","depth":12},{"id":301,"text":"Biden said .","depth":10},{"id":302,"text":"`` I admire him for it . ''","depth":9},{"id":303,"text":"British Prime Minister David Cameron said","depth":10},{"id":304,"text":"Benedict `` will be missed as a spiritual leader to millions. ``","depth":10},{"id":305,"text":"Cameron 's Irish counterpart , Enda Kenny , praised Benedict for decades of leadership and service , as well as his decision","depth":11},{"id":306,"text":"to resign .","depth":11},{"id":307,"text":"`` It reflects his profound sense of duty to the Church ,","depth":12},{"id":308,"text":"and also his deep appreciation of the unique pressures of spiritual leadership in the modern world , ''","depth":12},{"id":309,"text":"Kenny said in a prepared statement .","depth":11},{"id":310,"text":"Archbishop Vincent Nichols , the president of the Catholic Bishops ' Conference of England and Wales , said","depth":11},{"id":311,"text":"the decision `` shocked and surprised everyone . ''","depth":11},{"id":312,"text":"`` Yet , on reflection , I am sure","depth":12},{"id":313,"text":"that many will recognize it to be a decision of great courage and characteristic clarity of mind and action , ''","depth":12},{"id":314,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":315,"text":"`` It 's like watching your own Dad get old","depth":11},{"id":316,"text":"and admit","depth":13},{"id":317,"text":"he 's not up to all the duties","depth":14},{"id":318,"text":"that being the head of a family involves , ''","depth":14},{"id":319,"text":"Dolan said .","depth":12},{"id":320,"text":"`` And there 's a somberness ,","depth":11},{"id":321,"text":"there 's a sadness there . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":643,"left":0,"right":642,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":642,"left":452,"right":641,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":452,"left":351,"right":451,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":351,"left":328,"right":350,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":328,"left":327,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":327,"left":325,"right":326,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":325,"left":323,"right":324,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":323,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":324,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":326,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":350,"left":339,"right":349,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":339,"left":332,"right":338,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":332,"left":8,"right":331,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":331,"left":9,"right":330,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":330,"left":329,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":329,"left":